                              <msItem xml:id="p2_i1.7">
                                  <locus from="126r" to="145r"/>
                                  <title type="complete" ref="LIT4723TarikaWaldaAmid#Patriarchs"/>
                                  <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"></gap> ፶አንቀጽ፡ በእንተ፡
                                  አእምሮ፡ ስመ፡ ሊቃነ፡ ጳጳሳት፡ ዘግብጽ፡ ወምስር፡ እለ፡ ተሠይሙ፡ በእለ፡ እስክንድርያ፡ እምአብ፡ ሐዋርያ፡
                                  ማርቆስ፡ ወንጌላዊ፡ ወእስከ፡ አብ፡ አትናስዮስ፡ ዘአዕረፈ፡ ኀበ፡ ምሕረተ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ልዑል።</incipit>
                                  <note>This series is brought down to <persName ref="PRS4380Gabriel"></persName>,
                                (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ዘነበረ፡ በዘመነ፡
                                <persName ref="PRS6229LebnaDe">ልብነ፡ ድንግል፡</persName> ንጉሥ፡</foreign>).</note>
                                  </msItem>
                                  <msItem xml:id="p2_i1.8">
                                    <locus from="145r"></locus>
                                    <title type="complete" ref="LIT4723TarikaWaldaAmid#Councils" xml:lang="gez">
                                    አንቀጽ፡ ፶ወ፫ በእንተ፡ ተዝካረ፡ ጉባኤ።</title>
                                    <textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
                                  </msItem>
                                  <msItem xml:id="p2_i1.9">
                                    <locus from="154r"></locus>
                                    <title type="complete" ref="LIT4723TarikaWaldaAmid#MuslimRulers"></title>
                                    <textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
                                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">ዝውእቱ፡ አስማቲሆሙ፡ ለነገሥት፡ ዘተንባላት፡ እለ፡
                                    ነግሡ፡ በምስር፡ ወበግዳድ፡ እማሐመድ፡ እስከ፡ ዘመንነ፡ ዛቲ፡ ወእሙንቱኬ፡ ነገድ፡ እለ፡
                                  ይሰመዩ፡ እልእምውያ፡ ወእልባስያ፡ ወእልፍጥምያ፡ ወነገሥትሂ፡ እልአልዩብያ፡ ወካልኣኒሆሙ።</incipit>

                                  <msItem xml:id="p2_i1.9.1">
                                    <locus from="154r"></locus>
                                    <title type="complete" ref="LIT4723TarikaWaldaAmid#Caliphs"></title>
                                    <textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
                                  </msItem>
                                  <msItem xml:id="p2_i1.9.2">
                                    <locus from="156v"></locus>
                                    <title type="complete" ref="LIT4723TarikaWaldaAmid#Umayyads"></title>
                                    <textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
                                  </msItem>
                                  <msItem xml:id="p2_i1.9.3">
                                    <locus from="161r"></locus>
                                    <title type="complete" ref="LIT4723TarikaWaldaAmid#Abbasids"></title>
                                    <textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
                                    <note>Ending with
                                      <foreign xml:lang="gez">ምእትስም፡ በአላህ</foreign>.
                                    </note>
                                  </msItem>
                                  <msItem xml:id="p1_i2.9.4">
                                    <locus from="174v"></locus>
                                    <title type="complete" xml:lang="en">The Tulunides and other dynasties
                                    in Egypt</title>
                                    <textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
                                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">ነገሥት፡ እለ፡ ነግሡ፡ ላዕለ፡ ምስር፡ እምነ፡ አሕመድ፡
                                    ወልደ፡ ጡሉን፡ ወእስከ፡ ካፉር፡ ላእከ፡ እልእክሺድ፡</incipit>
                                  </msItem>
                                  <msItem xml:id="p1_i2.9.5">
                                    <locus from="183r"></locus>
                                    <title type="complete" ref="LIT4723TarikaWaldaAmid#Ayyubids"></title>
                                    <textLang mainLang="gez"></textLang>
                                  </msItem>
                                  <msItem xml:id="p1_i2.9.6">
